<h2 id="what-we-wont-publish">What we won't publish</h2>

<p>
  As we are an open source project, we try to only promote content that is free, or has a low barrier to entry. We're not too keen on partnership deals, promotions, or referral schemes.
</p>

<p>
  If we do list a product or service, it is because they have established credibility in the accessibility community.
